name: RETURN (luhyphenwai)
description:
RETURN 

humanity has fallen
its time to change that

CONTROLS:
WASD to move
Space to jump
E to interact (Move blocks, open doors, read articles)
F to time travel


Made in 15 days for a jam about time
Code: Lu-Wai Wong
Art: Raphael Kwok
Music and sound: Max Campbell
